   2.2. Prohibited Uses Without a Commercial License:
      2.2.1. Any commercial use as defined in Section 1.3.
      2.2.2. Team use without acquiring a team license.
      2.2.3. Use within businesses, non-profit organizations, or governmental entities, regardless of profit motive.
      2.2.4. Deployment of the Software in proprietary, internal, or revenue-generating systems.
   2.3. Team Licensing:
